    "text": "Thank you, Agent M."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.94,
    "endTime": 121.08,
    "text": "It's 'Pretty Woman', but she's Richard Gere and you're Julia Roberts."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.72,
    "endTime": 124.22,
    "text": "Honestly, this has been the best few weeks of my entire life."
  },
  {
